    "instructions_important": "false",
    "long_instructions": "#### Gemma's Song\r\n\r\nAn **algorithm** is a series of steps to accomplish a task. For example, your friend Gemma heard a great sound combination online and described it as:\r\n\r\n- First there were three sounds together, like a **Patter**, **Boom**, and **Cloud**\r\n- Then they repeated - the same three sounds!\r\n- But then the bass and lead changed - it sounded **funky** like the music was **funneling** into me\r\n\r\nFollow Gemma's **algorithm** to recreate her song. You can listen to her song below. Your song should match hers exactly!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/3899b4f06e1afcab08fa6080c0359192-image-1741387084637.37.44 PM.png)",
